text: WINNER is a South Korean band formed by YG Entertainment in 2014. The group debuted on August 14, 2014, as 5 members with the album, "2014 S/S," but went on hiatus due to arguements over creative differences. In 2016, the group returned with the EP, "EXIT:E," originally meant to be the first part of the "EXIT" series. Unfortunately, the series was cancelled after Taehyun departed on November 26, 2016, due to health issues.
